data.description: Fantastic corner lot colonial with 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths! Step inside to the recently added mudroom with shiplap walls and laminate flooring, the perfect drop zone for coats and shoes. The kitchen offers plenty of cabinet space plus a pantry for extra storage. The pantry was once a half bath and could be converted back if desired. Enjoy meals in the dining room complete with a built in server, chair rail and an open view into the living room with hardwood flooring. One of the bedrooms is on the main level, while three bedrooms with ceiling fans and hardwood floors are upstairs along with a full bath. Head to the lower level to find a family room with a gas fireplace and a convenient second full bath. Outside, you'll appreciate the nice sized fenced yard with raised garden beds and newly sided single car garage with additional parking space in the drive. This home has been well maintained and offers an abundance of updates! Updates include: dishwasher 2023; garage siding, refrigerator, washer, windows (with transferrable warranty) 2021; stove, A/C 2020; dryer 2019, roof (complete tear off) & furnace 2017; HWT 2014; and Ohio State Waterproofing  with sump-pump and battery back up 2013. Schedule your showing today!
